WEBVTT

00:00.280 --> 00:05.960
Couldn’t it be obvious that people see the same things and have the same ideas about them?

00:06.000 --> 00:12.170
If the perceived information is the same for two people and they think the same things about it, why would it be odd if those people produce the same impressions about what they see?

00:12.170 --> 00:15.260
We’re all human beings, after all.
